        Heavy Metal Death Pirate is a 2D action sidescroller taking place in   
        contemporary time                                                      
                                                                               
        The main feature of the game is that it mixes many different retro     
        gameplay styles in a single game. There are many unique characters to  
        choose from and they are divided into three different types of         
        gameplay: Shoot'em up, Run n' gun and Beat'em up.                      
                                                                               
        Of course, the whole game was designed with this in mind               
        and every stages can be completed with any kind of gameplay.           
                                                                               
        The game runs in 60 fps and will features 7 playable characters, 26    
        stages and an original storyline. The players can level up their       
        characters and upgrade their weapons.                                  
                                                                               
        The languages available are English and French.                        
                                                                               
                                                                               
